ngswitchuser extension installation instructions

Installation Steps
==================

1. Unpack/unzip

  Unpack the downloaded package into the 'extension' directory of your eZ Publish installation.

2. Activate extension

   Activate the extension by using the admin interface ( Setup -> Extensions ) or by
   prepending ngswitchuser to ActiveExtensions[] in settings/override/site.ini.append.php:

   [ExtensionSettings]
   ActiveExtensions[]=ngswitchuser

5. Clear caches for admin siteaccess

   Clear all caches (from admin 'Setup' tab or from command line).

7. Add users to selectbox

   For adding users to selectbox, grant access to "can_switch" function of "ngswitchuser" module to associated User / Userrole